Fred Morgan (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Morgan_(actor) 0 Fred Lees Morgan (June 1878 – 11 May 1941) was a British actor of the silent era.He was born in Islington, London, England, UK and died at age 62 in London.
